snippet.title: Matthias Wandel
snippet.description:
Videos about woodworking, taking more of an engineering perspective on things.

This channels started out as short videos to go with the articles on my website (http://woodgears.ca).  However, The videos views have since exceeded page views on my website.  But most videos still have a corresponding article on my website - see links in video descriptions.

My website: http://woodgears.ca

My odds and ends YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3_AWXcf2K3l9ILVuQe-XwQ

You can also follow me on instagram: https://www.instagram.com/matthiaswandel/

Please do NOT contact me about YouTube MCNs, mobile games, review for free product, or affiliate programs.  I am NOT interested.

Sorry I had to remove the email address from here because I get too much spam from companies wanting me to promote their products.
If you would like to contact me, please read the FAQ document at http://woodgears.ca/faq
